Responses.NAM1 - Response Text: The Ashlands are the dry, inhospitable wastelands surrounding the lower slopes of Red Mountain.
The Ashlands extend to the Sea of Ghosts to the north, and elsewhere form a wide margin between the blighted Red Mountain region and other geographic regions.
The town of Ald'ruhn and the village of Maar Gan are the only sizable permanent Ashlands settlements.
Ashlanders hunt for game here, and their herds find sparse grazing. It rains rarely, and suffers frequent ash storms.
